><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">RapidEye</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Market Review</h2> <p>The MSCI ACWI rose 2.23% during the quarter on the prospect of policy rate cuts in late 2024 and continued optimism around artificial intelligence (AI). The S&amp;P 500\u00ae rose 4.28%, with gains largely concentrated in the information technology and communication services</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155143368/image_155143368.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742319-bny-mellon-dynamic-total-return-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 17:07:00"}, {"id": "4742317", "title": "Powell Pulls No Punches", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1487901286/image_1487901286.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Boxer use various punch combinations, including the jab, hook, uppercut, cross, swing, straight. Getting in close to make opponent on ropes and knockout. Boxing champions win the round in boxing ring\" data-id=\"1487901286\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1487901286/image_1487901286.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1487901286/image_1487901286.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1487901286/image_1487901286.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1487901286/image_1487901286.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1487901286/image_1487901286.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1487901286/image_1487901286.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_